    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/0b203ae14e16977682e16a1f4e86fdce.webp?t=1674582929\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/f422b2eeb457b84a5d638e0592052304.poster.avif?t=1674582929\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/f422b2eeb457b84a5d638e0592052304.webm?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/f422b2eeb457b84a5d638e0592052304.mp4?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>BUNNY HOP HARE TRIGGER</strong> is a first person parkour race to the finish line that is designed from the ground up to be speedrun while also being accessible for those who just want to go <strong><i>FAST</i></strong>.<br><br>With 5 uniquely designed worlds for aesthetic variety, you can expect over 100 levels of <i>speedrunning bliss</i> as well as additional bonuses such as an Endless Runner mode and Free Roam!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/ffa7a294da0e4a7b8516e0d4ded1eafc.poster.avif?t=1674582929\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/ffa7a294da0e4a7b8516e0d4ded1eafc.webm?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/ffa7a294da0e4a7b8516e0d4ded1eafc.mp4?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>High speed and mobility</i> is the name of the game. With movement and air strafing inspired from <strong>classic FPS games</strong>, you will never be capped at what speed you can achieve. The better you get, the faster you go!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/c01cd6bb14c0e9631b5b1464f424a48d.poster.avif?t=1674582929\" width=600 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/c01cd6bb14c0e9631b5b1464f424a48d.webm?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/c01cd6bb14c0e9631b5b1464f424a48d.mp4?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress, you'll unlock more and more tools to help you in your quest of become the fastest being in the universe!<br><br>These tools range from:<br><br>-Grappling Hooks<br>-Rocket Launchers (for jumping, of course)<br>-Hang Gliders<br><br>And much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/385645ba50bf228b584ba117ebdb40ed.poster.avif?t=1674582929\" width=600 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/385645ba50bf228b584ba117ebdb40ed.webm?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285010/extras/385645ba50bf228b584ba117ebdb40ed.mp4?t=1674582929\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>Bunny Hop Hare Trigger</i> is still in active development, and is relying on community feedback to become the best it can possibly be. If the demo interests you, please consider joining the Discord and sharing your feedback!",
